答えなら「好きなだけ」が極まってく
If you want an answer, "as much as you like" is peaking

377
00:21:17,346 --> 00:21:20,546
1秒前 完全アップデート ya ya
One second ago, a complete update, ya ya

378
00:21:21,146 --> 00:21:24,046
不安グッバイ 自分以外は敵じゃない
Goodbye anxiety, nobody but myself is my enemy

379
00:21:24,446 --> 00:21:27,446
折り句ご無用 指を立てろ
No need for acrostics, raise your finger

380
00:21:28,246 --> 00:21:31,046
Ha~ 揺れろ運命
Ha~ shake, destiny

381
00:21:33,146 --> 00:21:34,846
Ah~ あたらしいウルトラC
Ah~ a new Ultra C

382
00:21:35,346 --> 00:21:38,246
その感情を燃料に
Using those emotions as fuel

383
00:21:38,546 --> 00:21:40,546
勝ちの確信 駆け上がってく
Certainty of victory, climbing up

384
00:21:41,046 --> 00:21:43,046
1秒前 完全アップデート ya ya
One second ago, a complete update, ya ya

385
00:21:43,546 --> 00:21:45,546
この生き様で Make some noise
Make some noise with this way of life

386
00:21:45,846 --> 00:21:48,846
見舞う We gotta 豪めく Go-Boy
Pay a visit, we gotta, brilliant Go-Boy

387
00:21:49,146 --> 00:21:52,346
宿した熱狂は伝播する
The passion you've harbored will spread

388
00:21:52,546 --> 00:21:54,046
幕開けは直後だ
The curtain rises right after

389
00:21:54,446 --> 00:21:56,546
貰うは大喝采
We'll receive a huge round of applause

390
00:21:56,846 --> 00:21:58,546
Ready? Get down!

391
00:22:00,546 --> 00:22:04,046
覚醒 アップデート hey
Waking up, update, hey

392
00:22:13,146 --> 00:22:15,546
独りきりじゃ just kidding
Being all alone? Just kidding

393
00:22:16,846 --> 00:22:19,546
決めてたから dreaming
Because I had decided, dreaming

394
00:22:20,546 --> 00:22:24,046
間違いだらけ勘違いもして
Full of mistakes and misunderstandings

395
00:22:24,546 --> 00:22:27,546
ときめきをリテイク
Retaking the excitement

396
00:22:28,146 --> 00:22:30,046
失っても continue
Even if I lose it, continue

397
00:22:30,246 --> 00:22:33,846
支払った対価の自分あの日の
The me that paid the price that day

398
00:22:34,146 --> 00:22:36,546
してないわけない後悔 胸に飾れ
Of course I have regrets, wear them on your chest

399
00:22:36,846 --> 00:22:37,846
前向き直せ
Face forward again

400
00:22:38,146 --> 00:22:39,346
捕らえて
Catch it

401
