信じてくれ
Believe me

403
00:22:50,146 --> 00:22:53,046
青くもゆる僕は仄々
Burning blue, I am faintly glowing

404
00:22:53,346 --> 00:22:57,046
時は経って 焦がれる心
Time passes, a yearning heart

405
