00:27:50,594 --> 00:27:53,994
最低か? やあもう本当最悪だだだだだだ
Are you the worst? Oh, it's really the worst-t-t-t-t-t

476
00:27:54,694 --> 00:27:58,294
寝ても覚めても付きまとう
Haunting me awake or asleep

477
00:27:58,394 --> 00:28:01,994
見える意識の裏側に
Behind the visible consciousness

478
00:28:02,094 --> 00:28:05,694
大きく開いた黒い穴
A big open black hole

479
00:28:05,794 --> 00:28:09,194
分かる 分かる 分かる
I understand, I understand, I understand

480
00:28:09,394 --> 00:28:10,994
いいっす 許せん
It's okay, unforgivable

481
00:28:10,994 --> 00:28:12,694
許す 許せん
Forgive, unforgivable

482
00:28:12,694 --> 00:28:15,794
かわいい えへへ ふふん 怖い
Cute, ehehe, hmph, scary

