行動 名も持たず
Action, without even a name

495
00:28:56,394 --> 00:28:58,094
狂騒 意味もなく
Uproar, without any meaning

496
00:28:58,194 --> 00:29:01,494
永劫 自己満足
Eternal self-satisfaction

497
