昔々のお甘えつき
Once upon a time, a pampered child

503
00:29:27,494 --> 00:29:31,094
前向き前向きのひとだかり
A forward-looking crowd

504
00:29:31,194 --> 00:29:34,794
無邪気無敵の生まれつき
Innocent and invincible by birth

505
