それが それが それが
That is, that is, that is

506
00:29:38,394 --> 00:29:41,794
責任集合体
Responsibility Society

507
00:29:41,794 --> 00:29:45,094
アンタもワタシも関係ない
It has nothing to do with you or me

508
00:29:45,194 --> 00:29:48,594
責任集合体
Responsibility Society

